{"title":"向朝鲜弟兄们欢呼","authors":["申述"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":7,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"向朝鲜弟兄们欢呼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"申述"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我向你们欢呼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝鲜弟兄们！战友们！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们和我们一样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从血和泪的历史中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学会了自己做主人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三十六年了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凝结着苦难和仇恨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在鲜血铺平的道路上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们雄壮的进军了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勇敢的战友呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们个个是钢铁化身。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从金川打过汉城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从襄阳打到蔚珍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在山岳、海湾，城市和乡村，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在你们的国土上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敲响战鼓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃起了解放的火焰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弟兄们！战友们！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看见了你们。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在你们祖国的天空、海洋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在那辽阔的大地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们奋勇前进的身影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往南，往南，一直往南！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前进呀！战友们！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把你们在东北密林中的勇敢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把你们在华北原野上的坚强，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全部捧献出来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向人民的自由，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向子孙的幸福，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向祖国的彻底解放。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们——中国和全世界的人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都眼望着朝鲜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为你们的勇敢欢呼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为你们的胜利欢呼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们是愤怒的海涛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们是正义的风暴；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在你们面前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么帝国主义全站不住脚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么卖国贼全要狼狈奔逃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我向你们欢呼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝鲜弟兄们！战友们！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不停地往南呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和我们一样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不停地往南呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到海洋之滨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到祖国最后一寸疆土。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五○年七月五日"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}